  • 2 year diploma or 4 year degree programs
  • cheaper, smaller class sizes
  • most subjects focus on application over theory uni:
  • only 4 year degree programs plus Master's and PhD
  • usually way bigger class sizes and campuses
  • more expensive
  • classes focus a lot more on theory and research than application and practice
